Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.75,0:00:03.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.29,0:00:07.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上周已经要你们先读一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.21,0:00:12.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教材的153页到162页当做作业了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.86,0:00:15.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  大概就是这样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.69,0:00:19.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伦又在打瞌睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.02,0:00:20.24,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始上课吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.50,0:00:24.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有过这样的事呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.21,0:00:28.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我这也不是白当伦的朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.19,0:00:32.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伦  烤薄饼做好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.14,0:00:37.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优子  烤薄饼在哪里啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.49,0:00:40.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伦  声音太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.42,0:00:42.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  那边  有点吵哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.36,0:00:45.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.44,0:00:48.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优子  你还太嫩了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.83,0:00:53.71,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}小考
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.52,0:00:59.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这题好难哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.59,0:01:02.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法  解下一题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.89,0:01:04.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要放弃！ 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.42,0:01:09.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了  试着把这道题当做人生的问题吧  
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.56,0:01:11.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果同样没有解决而逃避掉的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.96,0:01:13.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会变成怎样呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.47,0:01:20.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都有着无论什么困难都能克服的力量哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.63,0:01:26.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去唤醒吧  沉睡在你心中的炽热灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.40,0:01:29.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们一定能做得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.04,0:01:33.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咔嚓？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.28,0:01:34.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咔嚓？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.11,0:01:35.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咔嚓
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.38,0:01:38.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咔嚓…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.65,0:01:40.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.38,0:01:44.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼头老师在上课时受伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.22,0:01:47.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,体育课？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.26,0:01:48.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是数学课
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.87,0:01:51.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数学…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.14,0:03:26.95,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(350,240)\fs40}超大份烤薄饼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.05,0:03:31.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然在上课时受伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.96,0:03:33.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没资格当老师啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.00,0:03:34.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.92,0:03:38.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼头  听说你手受伤了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.82,0:03:40.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  我帮你泡了咖啡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.98,0:03:42.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是顺便泡的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.14,0:03:45.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  镰手老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.72,0:03:49.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  让我拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.64,0:03:51.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要勉强  老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.42,0:03:54.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那柚多谷也来拿点什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.74,0:03:55.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.60,0:04:00.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家变成了我的双手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.50,0:04:02.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真是无比幸福的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.73,0:04:04.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我来贴身保护吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.72,0:04:06.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不必了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.47,0:04:09.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  我明明是担心你而来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.22,0:04:11.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的担心我才不要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.90,0:04:13.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是还帮你缠了绷带吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.33,0:04:15.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那是另一回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.02,0:04:18.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你瞧  绷带下面是不是很痒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.42,0:04:20.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.97,0:04:22.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始上课
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.18,0:04:27.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次关于189页的公式进行了简单讲解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.38,0:04:29.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次我们来证明它
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.67,0:04:34.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为教师怎么能输给这点小痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.94,0:04:36.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.82,0:04:41.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  老师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.70,0:04:42.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.89,0:04:45.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来替您写黑板吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.21,0:04:48.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.85,0:04:53.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别被粉笔灰弄脏了  穿上白大衣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.59,0:04:54.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.96,0:05:06.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个可以有！ 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.75,0:05:09.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们继续上课
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.10,0:05:12.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,173页的第二章
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.91,0:05:15.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先从第一个公式的证明开始
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.00,0:05:19.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.34,0:05:23.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在笑什么  请安静
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.66,0:05:34.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然拖了特地来帮我的学生的后腿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.09,0:05:35.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.12,0:05:40.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说您受伤了  没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.97,0:05:47.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能这样  纪美子  不能过分让学生担心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.90,0:05:51.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题  你们看  已经快好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.66,0:05:56.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不痛 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.89,0:05:58.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.78,0:06:00.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.53,0:06:01.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.86,0:06:08.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  老师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.79,0:06:11.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透同学  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.42,0:06:15.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好  交得晚了真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.77,0:06:17.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把之前的作业带来…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.67,0:06:21.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.74,0:06:22.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.64,0:06:23.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.34,0:06:23.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.95,0:06:24.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.16,0:06:29.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  手机的铃声忘关了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.31,0:06:30.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作业呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.25,0:06:31.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下我拿给您
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.89,0:06:35.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就觉得怎么这么重  什么时候进来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.42,0:06:40.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在在上课  也不能交给谁来看着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.84,0:06:43.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只好先回家了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.06,0:06:45.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.49,0:06:50.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是透家的猫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.35,0:06:52.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.74,0:06:57.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让柚多谷也抱抱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.73,0:07:03.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什么名字呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.14,0:07:04.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碳酸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.15,0:07:06.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碳酸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.38,0:07:07.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是电池啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.93,0:07:09.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.50,0:07:10.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那就是果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.85,0:07:11.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.00,0:07:13.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是果汁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.69,0:07:15.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好哦  果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.92,0:07:16.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.13,0:07:21.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碳酸好可爱啊  真是只漂亮的猫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.94,0:07:23.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次我还想摸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.61,0:07:24.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.82,0:07:28.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  找到去透家的借口了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.16,0:07:33.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚多谷我也想摸个痛快
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.60,0:07:35.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.73,0:07:39.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到本人同意了  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.30,0:07:43.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黏住黏住黏住…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.21,0:07:43.28,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说你不去透家了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.92,0:07:48.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  你回家了一趟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.35,0:07:51.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  第一节课没有上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.33,0:07:55.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说啊  这种时间就该坐出租车啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.95,0:08:00.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩真可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.87,0:08:02.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把球给我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.03,0:08:08.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透  我来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.43,0:08:09.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优子  给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.22,0:08:11.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透  没关系啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.68,0:08:12.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优子给我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.72,0:08:13.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,球…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.09,0:08:16.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.64,0:08:17.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了算了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.70,0:08:21.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  姐姐的胸部好大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.47,0:08:26.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又松又软的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.51,0:08:27.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别摸啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.54,0:08:31.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  不要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.62,0:08:35.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是糖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.95,0:08:39.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说透是很喜欢小孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.79,0:08:44.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  不用东西来引诱也可以啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.59,0:08:48.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让透你去还球吧  去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.53,0:08:54.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游玩设施  好怀念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.01,0:08:56.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.28,0:09:01.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下来啦  丢脸死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.85,0:09:03.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好玩啊  你看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.77,0:09:05.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都说了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.73,0:09:10.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然这么说  小渚不也坐上去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.44,0:09:12.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是当长凳坐的啦  长凳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.10,0:09:16.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊  住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.79,0:09:23.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.47,0:09:27.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么晚打电话抱歉啊  现在能接吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.91,0:09:29.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.93,0:09:35.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在想之前渚想要借的CD是哪张来着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.62,0:09:38.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就拿第二张给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.29,0:09:41.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在忙什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.37,0:09:42.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  没干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.88,0:09:44.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  别装啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.73,0:09:47.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了没在做什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.95,0:09:51.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.44,0:09:52.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.36,0:10:08.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快说明天见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.76,0:10:11.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我不知道什么时候挂断才好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.63,0:10:14.05,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}\N\N\N\N\N\N痊\N愈\N了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.55,0:10:18.09,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}\N\N\N\N\N\N\N于\N是\N于\N是\N
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.28,0:10:18.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以把积攒的诗写完啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.88,0:10:25.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸽子模仿得好像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.95,0:10:47.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞  瘦了一点点！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.67,0:10:55.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉腿也稍微细了一点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.51,0:11:00.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  小渚的腿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.12,0:11:04.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被发现了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.90,0:11:07.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里居然有颗痣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.52,0:11:09.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.65,0:11:10.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.97,0:11:11.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别趁机偷看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.61,0:11:18.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家附近的百货店里面好像开了一家新的咖啡店
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.78,0:11:20.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起去吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.52,0:11:24.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里的超大份烤薄饼好像很有名
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.97,0:11:25.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超大份！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.57,0:11:27.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.89,0:11:29.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真难得你这么有干劲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.90,0:11:32.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就这个礼拜六去怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.58,0:11:35.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超大份
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.85,0:11:39.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超大份
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.84,0:11:43.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好哎  那我就从早上开始一直空着肚子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.04,0:11:46.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以不好好吃早饭哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.62,0:11:53.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好兴奋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.50,0:11:56.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电梯  快点来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.69,0:11:57.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好期待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.90,0:12:07.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…是几楼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.40,0:12:08.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六楼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.33,0:12:09.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.43,0:12:11.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是假日好挤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.98,0:12:15.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小渚  快点快点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.64,0:12:19.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…是那个被称为「FLAG」的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.81,0:12:21.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有很不好的预感
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.12,0:12:25.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.94,0:12:28.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于已经瘦掉点的我来说  是不会被淘汰的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.66,0:12:35.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  给我记住了  我爬楼梯还不行嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.76,0:12:37.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.10,0:12:47.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小渚  你好快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.22,0:12:51.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  所有的准备都做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.55,0:12:53.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.59,0:12:57.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.12,0:13:00.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去好不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.10,0:13:04.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临  是四位客人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.50,0:13:05.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.73,0:13:07.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么请往这边走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.00,0:13:11.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店员小姐的制服真可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.97,0:13:15.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透  把衣服叠好放在那边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.49,0:13:16.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.45,0:13:20.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这菜单做得真细致啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.48,0:13:21.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.12,0:13:25.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚好不用排队就可以进来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.52,0:13:27.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们要喝什么饮料
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.67,0:13:30.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里红茶的种类也好多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.07,0:13:33.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以点一壶叫她们拿过来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.02,0:13:35.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚你喝什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.14,0:13:46.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总…总之比起红茶来  我想先喝水…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.74,0:13:48.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大杯的水…拜托你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.91,0:13:49.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.94,0:13:52.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  请给我们水
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.39,0:13:56.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就点这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.90,0:13:57.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪个哪个？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.13,0:14:00.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要超大份烤薄饼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.72,0:14:03.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么好不容易来一次  那我就点这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.33,0:14:07.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们就点不同的东西  然后交换着吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.57,0:14:08.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.43,0:14:12.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  我们要点单
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.54,0:14:14.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  现在就过来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.93,0:14:17.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你们久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.72,0:14:20.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀是透同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.21,0:14:21.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美保
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.20,0:14:24.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在这里打工哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.67,0:14:26.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说柚多谷也在这里打工…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.24,0:14:30.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也不是什么时候都在一起的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.14,0:14:31.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透  稍微让开一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.95,0:14:33.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.76,0:14:38.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是透的同学吧   谢谢你平时一直照顾她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.63,0:14:43.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不  都是她照顾我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.65,0:14:47.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透同学在一年级的女生里是很受欢迎的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.86,0:14:50.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说她很帅气又可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.20,0:14:51.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.82,0:14:56.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班上的同学经常提到她  还会介绍给老师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.24,0:14:57.13,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说我要超大份烤薄饼两个  
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.19,0:14:58.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浆果蛋糕一个  抹茶蛋糕一个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.71,0:15:00.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大吉岭和热的锡兰高地奶茶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.66,0:15:03.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外加阿萨姆红茶两杯  一份加柠檬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.48,0:15:05.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  请让我和您确认下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.14,0:15:07.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超大份烤薄饼两个  
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.43,0:15:08.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浆果蛋糕一个  抹茶蛋糕一个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.87,0:15:10.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大吉岭和热的锡兰高地奶茶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.54,0:15:13.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外加阿萨姆红茶两杯  一份加柠檬对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.09,0:15:16.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好能干的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.94,0:15:23.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临  十分抱歉  现在满座了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.53,0:15:27.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待时间啊  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.27,0:15:33.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位客人真是十分抱歉  再过二十分钟左右就有位子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.85,0:15:39.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好困扰啊  我现在就想喝到热热的红茶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.22,0:15:41.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚多谷我不知道能不能等得了二十分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.23,0:15:45.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一小会儿你可以等的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.06,0:15:47.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丰～大～人～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.02,0:15:53.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店员不能揪人脸的  美宝莲好过分
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.99,0:15:55.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就乖乖给我坐在那边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.95,0:15:59.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没到我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.19,0:16:03.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是让她打扰透和前辈们用餐就不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.46,0:16:06.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能要把柚多谷安排到比较远的位置才好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.16,0:16:08.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美宝莲  你有什么瞒着我的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.36,0:16:11.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你突然说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.32,0:16:12.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.88,0:16:14.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧  发现了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.47,0:16:22.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又把胸弄小了啊  这件制服一眼就看出来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.85,0:16:25.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.84,0:16:30.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你要来也不要挑店里最忙的时候来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.41,0:16:32.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用给你服务也可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.68,0:16:37.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是今天柚多谷是来支援美宝莲的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.09,0:16:39.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.03,0:16:46.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜单菜单  点什么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.82,0:16:45.99,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要点些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.54,0:16:48.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好贵…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.97,0:16:50.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.22,0:16:53.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只要份…本日的红茶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.04,0:16:56.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是工作日才能喝到的红茶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.82,0:17:01.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烤薄饼蛋糕快点来呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.57,0:17:03.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好期待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.37,0:17:04.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你们久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.34,0:17:05.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.45,0:17:08.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好强大的分量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.73,0:17:11.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看过去好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.00,0:17:14.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超大份烤薄饼也快来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.56,0:17:18.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…那个就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.84,0:17:36.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种店慢慢地品味红茶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.01,0:17:38.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有种大人的感觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.53,0:17:42.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人吗  我还真不想当大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.06,0:17:44.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想一直待在学校里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.87,0:17:45.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.93,0:17:48.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还想快点长大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.52,0:17:53.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人…我可以成为大人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.41,0:17:54.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们认为呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.89,0:17:56.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.61,0:18:03.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透还真能吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.71,0:18:07.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透  居然在这个地方偶遇你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.97,0:18:10.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感觉这都是命运的安排
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.40,0:18:16.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不说话  柚多谷做了什么坏事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.95,0:18:22.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.47,0:18:25.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  她现在在咀嚼中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.11,0:18:29.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚多谷发现了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.80,0:18:34.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们初中就是同一所学校的啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.81,0:18:38.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚多谷和美宝莲也是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.81,0:18:42.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是美宝莲不在  她就不能妨碍我了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.25,0:18:45.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店员很忙真是悲剧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.07,0:18:46.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚多谷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.03,0:18:49.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  店员小姐  咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.21,0:18:51.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来妨碍你了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.97,0:18:53.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  你工作怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.72,0:18:55.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经到了换班时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.72,0:18:56.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家了  柚多谷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.35,0:18:59.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  你们慢慢享用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.96,0:19:04.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透…学校再见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.36,0:19:07.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透的班级也蛮有趣的  
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.68,0:19:09.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是个活泼的孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.43,0:19:15.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,升上二年级以后还能在一个班就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.87,0:21:09.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再过不久  二号线电车就要靠站了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.19,0:21:12.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要乘坐这班电车的请准备好上车了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.62,0:21:19.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很想尝尝小伦和烤薄饼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.15,0:21:24.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.72,0:21:28.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次在家里也试着做做烤薄饼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.58,0:21:32.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比这好吃的东西我认为没那么容易做出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.04,0:21:34.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.94,0:21:40.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没这回事  我有自信比这家店可以做得更好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.02,0:23:21.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不是说过不要妨碍透同学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.47,0:23:22.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.92,0:23:26.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烤薄饼好好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.06,0:23:30.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我说了不要在忙的时候来店里嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.22,0:23:33.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我请你吃好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.50,0:23:36.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美…美宝莲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.37,0:23:39.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是听好了  只有在店里不忙的时候哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.61,0:23:41.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的好的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.25,0:23:42.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回复一次就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.56,0:23:43.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.90,0:23:44.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别拉长
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.03,0:23:45.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.86,0:23:48.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  美宝莲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.54,0:23:49.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.35,0:23:51.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那制服很适合你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.90,0:23:52.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.90,0:23:54.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意图太简单易懂了点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.38,0:23:59.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好  柚多谷和美宝莲都好好表现了一番呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.84,0:24:00.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都看到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.93,0:24:03.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集我们也还会好好表现的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.72,0:24:06.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集A频道  +Smile
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.25,0:24:07.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「在绘马上祈愿」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.25,0:24:07.31,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}注：绘马即为在神社祈祷或者还愿时挂在寺社内绘画木板
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.57,0:24:08.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,频道就保持这样
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.93,0:24:10.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是OVA啊
